projects table:
---------------
project,
name,
created by,
start_date,
due_date,
priority,
assigned_to,
status,
description

issues table:
------------
project
created_by
create_date
priority
num_comments

comments table:
--------------
issue_id
comment_by
comment
comment_date

sub-project table:
-----------------
project_id
name,
time_required,
depends_on [list of sub-projects]
assigned to

goalpost table:
---------------
project_id
name
date_due
sub-projects-deliverable


